OL,6,GAnother week...another round of
OL,7,Gspeculation about BBC U-turns.
OL,9,FMonday sees the official launch of
OL,10,Fthe new BBC News channel.
OL,12,FIt remains to be seen just how much
OL,13,FUK News will be included but it
OL,14,Fsounds like there will be more than
OL,15,Foriginally envisaged.
OL,17,FThe principal bespoke UK content will
OL,18,Fbe the main BBC One bulletins,
OL,19,FBreakfast, Newsnight and ` at some
OL,20,Fpoint soon ` Nicky Campbell's 5 Live
OL,21,Fshow.
OL,3,CBBC News changes and possible BBC
OL,4,CFour U-turn
