OL,6,FThe big test is the coverage of
OL,7,Fstories which are important within
OL,8,Fthe UK but of little international
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,FBad weather? Strikes? Court cases?
OL,12,FStories from the nations and regions?
OL,14,FThe death of Paul O'Grady last week
OL,15,Fwas a textbook example of the kind of
OL,16,Fdilemma which will arise.
OL,18,FWhat will be the threshold for the UK
OL,19,Fstream breaking away?
OL,3,CBBC News changes and possible BBC
OL,4,CFour U-turn
