OL,6,FLet's take a few weeks to judge the
OL,7,Fnew channel and not let sadness at
OL,8,Fchanges to the presentation rota and
OL,9,Fthe departure of some staff skew our
OL,10,Fjudgement.
OL,12,FIf the new channel works out, we may
OL,13,Fcome to wonder what the fuss was
OL,14,Fabout ` however hard it was for
OL,15,Findividuals and you can never
OL,16,Foverstate what it is like for anyone
OL,17,Fwhose job is under threat.
OL,3,CBBC News changes and possible BBC
OL,4,CFour U-turn
