OL,6,FIf the channel seems like a bland
OL,7,Foffering focused on the international
OL,8,Faudience and divorced from licence
OL,9,Fpayers, this could become a corporate
OL,10,Fcatastrophe.
OL,12,FThe decision though to simulcast
OL,13,FNewsnight on the new channel should
OL,14,Fbe welcomed ` even if there is still
OL,15,Fregret at the loss of the paper
OL,16,Freview.
OL,18,FIn recent years, Newsnight has
OL,19,Fsometimes felt adrift despite some
OL,20,Fexcellent content. On the news
OL,21,Fchannel it may reach more of its
OL,22,Fnatural audience.
OL,3,CBBC News changes and possible BBC
OL,4,CFour U-turn
