OL,6,FThere was a previous attempt a few
OL,7,Fyears ago to show Newsnight on the
OL,8,Fnews channel, delayed by a few
OL,9,Fminutes from the BBC Two screening.
OL,10,FIt didn't last long.
OL,12,FThe other bit of speculation concerns
OL,13,Frumours BBC Four will be spared the
OL,14,Faxe as a linear channel.
OL,16,FIt is noted that it gets a bigger
OL,17,Faudience than the revived BBC Three,
OL,18,Fat a lower cost.
