OL,6,FFor many of us, there is a logic
OL,7,Fabout turning a channel which is
OL,8,Fincreasingly like a curated selection
OL,9,Ffrom the archives into a streaming
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FIf linear TV is to survive it has to
OL,13,Ffocus on live output and big events `
OL,14,Fthe sense that there is a reason for
OL,15,Fwatching Happy Valley or Great
OL,16,FExpectations at 9pm on Sundays as
OL,17,Fpart of a collective, shared
OL,18,Fexperience. That sense of major
OL,19,Fchannels like BBC One or Two being
OL,20,Fspecial places.
OL,3,CBBC News changes and possible BBC
OL,4,CFour U-turn
